OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779286285
OL,3,CManchester City draw with Bournemouth
OL,4,Cto hand Arsenal Premier League title
OL,6,FManchester City's Premier League title
OL,7,Fhopes are over after defeat to
OL,8,FBournemouth handed Arsenal the title.
OL,10,FThe Blues were far from their best
OL,11,Fagainst a Cherries side who secured
OL,12,FEuropean football with the win and may
OL,13,Fyet earn a place in the Champions
OL,14,FLeague.
OL,16,FJunior Kroupi scored the only goal of
OL,17,Fthe game shortly before half-time and
OL,18,Fwhile City had chances, they couldn't
OL,19,Ffind a leveller until the dying stages
OL,20,Fthrough Erling Haaland and that was
OL,21,Ftoo little too late.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
