OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779286285
OL,3,CManchester City draw with Bournemouth
OL,4,Cto hand Arsenal Premier League title
OL,6,FTuesday's result on the south coast
OL,7,Fleaves Mikel Arteta's men four points
OL,8,Fclear of City before the final round
OL,9,Fof games take place on Sunday, with
OL,10,Fthe Gunners set to lift the trophy at
OL,11,FCrystal Palace.
OL,13,FBuild-up to this game had been
OL,14,Fovershadowed by dramatic reports that
OL,15,FGuardiola is set to step down as City
OL,16,Fmanager at the end of this season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
