FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779286285
OL,3,CManchester City draw with Bournemouth
OL,4,Cto hand Arsenal Premier League title
OL,6,FHe told television broadcasters before
OL,7,Fthe game that speculation over his
OL,8,Ffuture had "absolutely zero" impact on
OL,9,Fpreparations, but his side were
OL,10,Foutplayed and outfought by the
OL,11,Fbrilliant Cherries, who extended their
OL,12,Funbeaten run to 17 matches.
OL,14,FIn a post-match interview following
OL,15,Fthe defeat Guardiola would not be
OL,16,Fdrawn on his future and said he would
OL,17,Fhave to speak to the chairman, his
OL,18,Fteam and family first.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
